headline: Will TE Connectivity (TEL) Beat Estimates Again in Its Next Earnings Report?

headline: CTS (CTS) Q3 Earnings Lag Estimates
summary: CTS (CTS) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -1.64% and +4.82%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
